content:
Taking Action Based on Intelligence Signals

Automate actions based on intelligence signals detected by your telephony system. For example, if the customer is unhappy during a support call, Service Cloud Voice can show a Next Best Action recommendation.

Available in: Salesforce Classic, Lightning Experience
Available with these telephony models:
Service Cloud Voice with Amazon Connect
Service Cloud Voice with Partner Telephony from Amazon Connect
Service Cloud Voice with Partner Telephony

Build a flow that maps detected signals to an action defined in Salesforce. This can send notifications, show a script, recommend a strategy, or complete any other action.

Use Next Best Action recommendations to show agents what to do next based on the current conversation. Recommendations are based on intelligence signals defined in your telephony system.

Use auto-launched flows to run small-to-complex business processes and perform quick actions.

Prepare Your Telephony System for Conversation Intelligence
Create a rule in Salesforce that triggers an action based on intelligence signals defined in your telephony system.

Automatically Trigger an Action Based on a Conversation Intelligence Signal
